<item>
            <title>[LU-7752] All packages to configure Lustre on centos 7</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7752</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi Team,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Myself Ajit Tate.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am working as system administrator from past 2 years in an animation studio.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would like to know steps involved in configuring lustre file system on centos 7.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We already have lustre file system which is running on centos 6.5 (server and client)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And we are now upgrading client machines i.e. from centos 6.5 to centos 7&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So kindly request you to guide us to configure lustre on centos 7.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks in advance.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
